data.description: *DIAMOND IN THE ROUGH* Unique home on 4.4 acres. Wrap around porch 8 foot wide surrounds this 2 story dwelling. Main living area on 2nd floor features an open Kitchen/Dining/Living combo. Lots of kitchen cabinets & center island. All appliances in place. Plenty of room for cooking your favorite meals & entertaining. Gas fireplace in living area. Split bedroom floor plan for more privacy. Master bedroom features French doors to the outside. Master bathroom w/ double vanity sinks, Jacuzzi tub, separate shower & walk-in closet. First level is your utility room w/ a window AC unit. Nice size screen room for an additional hang out spot. Home is in need of some TLC so bring your imagination & make this your HOME SWEET HOME today! Lots of potential!
